      <title>monte carlo</title>
      <link href="/2022/06/18/monte-carlo/"/>
      <url>/2022/06/18/monte-carlo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="简述"><a href="#简述" class="headerlink" title="简述"></a>简述</h1><p>蒙特卡罗方法是一种用多次取样来逐渐逼近样本真实分布的方法。与大数定律和中心极限定理有一定的相似之处。<br></p><p>另外蒙特卡罗并不是人的名字，而是位于摩纳哥的一个赌场的名字。</p><h1 id="简单的例子"><a href="#简单的例子" class="headerlink" title="简单的例子"></a>简单的例子</h1><p>最经典的例子应该是几何概型中的算’$\pi$’的数值。也就是高中课本上的撒豆子问题。<br></p><p>通过多次随机取样，取样点会随机分布在一个正方形的区域里，然后在该区域中画圆，就会是样本分成两部分。一部分在圆内，另一部分在圆外。然后通过算圆内的样本数占总样本数的比例可以近似算的圆的面积，最后通过圆面积公式能算得$\pi$的取值。</p><h2 id="实操"><a href="#实操" class="headerlink" title="实操"></a>实操</h2><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">(\frac{1}{4}S =\frac{1}{4}\pi R^{2} = \frac{n}{N}) \\ n:圆内区域的样本数 \\ N:样本总数</script></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import random</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sampleNum = 10000</span><br><span class="line">counter = 0</span><br><span class="line">plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">x1 = list()</span><br><span class="line">y1 = list()</span><br><span class="line">x2 = list()</span><br><span class="line">y2 = list()</span><br><span class="line">for i in range(sampleNum):</span><br><span class="line">    x = random.random()</span><br><span class="line">    y = random.random()</span><br><span class="line">    if x**2 + y**2 &lt; 1:</span><br><span class="line">        counter += 1</span><br><span class="line">        x1.append(x)</span><br><span class="line">        y1.append(y)</span><br><span class="line">    else:</span><br><span class="line">        x2.append(x)</span><br><span class="line">        y2.append(y)</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">print(4*counter/sampleNum)</span><br><span class="line">plt.scatter(x2, y2, color=&#x27;b&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">plt.scatter(x1, y1, color=&#x27;r&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="../post_figures/20220618_01.png" alt="fig1"></p>]]></content>
      
      
